{
  "title": "ISic003562. Fragmentary stone inscription",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: <a href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/F2GG87EQ\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/F2GG87EQ</a></div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]Α <span dir=\"ltr\">(vac.2)</span> EIΔEKV <span dir=\"ltr\">(vac.)</span>  <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]Ν <span dir=\"ltr\">(vac.2)</span> ΓΓΝΗ <span dir=\"ltr\">(vac.)</span>  <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">.</span>Ν <span dir=\"ltr\">(vac.2)</span> ΩΜΓ <span dir=\"ltr\">(vac.)</span>  <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]ΣΚ <span dir=\"ltr\">(vac.2)</span> ΣΣΤΟΣ <span dir=\"ltr\">(vac.)</span>  <br id=\"al5-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]ΟΝΟΣΠ̣ΟΚΑΙ <br id=\"al6-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]ΧΣΟΡΟΦΑΝΕ <br id=\"al7-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">7</span>ΚΛΕΗ <span dir=\"ltr\">(vac.2)</span> ΤΟΣΑΝΕ[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al8-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">8</span>Α <span dir=\"ltr\">(vac.2)</span> Σ <span dir=\"ltr\">(vac.)</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: <a href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/F2GG87EQ\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/F2GG87EQ</a></div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]Α&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;EIΔEKV&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]Ν&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;ΓΓΝΗ&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">·</span>Ν&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;ΩΜΓ&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]ΣΚ&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;ΣΣΤΟΣ&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]ΟΝΟΣ.ΟΚΑΙ<br id=\"al6-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]ΧΣΟΡΟΦΑΝΕ<br id=\"al7-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">7</span>ΚΛΕΗ&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;ΤΟΣΑΝΕ[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al8-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">8</span>Α&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Σ&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text of SEG based upon the drawing in DiStefano (non vidi)</span></span>; </li><li><span class=\"3\">3: <span>SEG: second letter is Ν or Μ</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2> translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>DiStefano presents a full restoration of the text, as an epitaph, but SEG is very sceptical and prints the visible letters only, as here.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 52.0930 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a></li><li> Distefano 2002 102 n.54, 100 fig.12, 106 no.11 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002018\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002018</a></li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
  "divs": [
    {
      "id": "editions",
